QuestData.Title: Disarmed and Docile
QuestData.Description:
There's a frankly unnerving amount of weaponry being waved about up there. Relieving them of some should help calm things down. Or at least calm my nerves.
What are they going to do without weapons, after all? Attack you with their bare hands? Ha!
QuestData.RewardText: Oh, those? Just dump them anywhere. I'm sure the elementals won't mind.
